                <img src="/images/refresh-current-row-in-ig/Snap1.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
            </div><p>In my current project I use an interactive grid on one page. When you click on a row, i. e. select it, a report is displayed below the grid that displays this data set. The editing of the data set is realized in a modal dialog. If it is closed, the report including the currently selected line in the grid should be updated.</p>]]></description></item></channel></rss>